**Decisions**
- Chose ordering fix over dual-pass for the location bug: simplest correct solution
- Companions are full party members with stat blocks, not narrative-only: per user preference
- Scene facts capped at 50 with FIFO: balances memory vs context window size
- World enrichment triggered automatically (not manual): the user wants the "world alive" effect
- NPC archival at 20-turn threshold: long enough to not lose recently-relevant NPCs, short enough to prevent bloat
- `reactToPartyHistory` every 5 turns: frequent enough to feel reactive, infrequent enough to not be costly